Still Open All Hours: Episode 1

A day in the life of the shop and its customers is followed including former Nurse Gladys Emmanuel and the Black Widow. Granville tries to secure a date with old flame Mavis without her terrifying sister Madge finding out. Leroy refuses to use the old delivery bike and comes up with an altogether more attractive way to deliver the orders.
